to\": 1510}, {\"ngram\": \"the tournament\", \"from\": 1526, \"to\": 1540}, {\"ngram\": \"the highlight\", \"from\": 1574, \"to\": 1587}, {\"ngram\": \"his career\", \"from\": 1591, \"to\": 1601}, {\"ngram\": \"that point\", \"from\": 1605, \"to\": 1615}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 30 major championship starts, Schauffele now has 15 top-10 finishes, an impressive run that was getting frustrating in some ways.\", \"from\": 1657, \"to\": 1789, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"30 major championship starts\", \"from\": 1660, \"to\": 1688}, {\"ngram\": \"Schauffele\", \"from\": 1690, \"to\": 1700}, {\"ngram\": \"15 top-10 finishes\", \"from\": 1709, \"to\": 1727}, {\"ngram\": \"an impressive run\", \"from\": 1729, \"to\": 1746}, {\"ngram\": \"some ways\", \"from\": 1779, \"to\": 1788}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Earlier this year, Schauffele had been in the final group of a tournament on four occasions without winning any of them.\", \"from\": 1790, \"to\": 1910, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Schauffele\", \"from\": 1809, \"to\": 1819}, {\"ngram\": \"the final group\", \"from\": 1832, \"to\": 1847}, {\"ngram\": \"a tournament\", \"from\": 1851, \"to\": 1863}, {\"ngram\": \"four occasions\", \"from\": 1867, \"to\": 1881}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But a switch to coach Chris Como late last year\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094Schauffele had worked almost exclusively under his father\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094ended up being the missing piece that made the difference.\", \"from\": 1912, \"to\": 2080, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1940, \"end\": 1944, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Como_1907\", \"score\": 0.9714838883207879, \"rank\": 0.015805100026760138, \"text\": \"Como\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Como_1907\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Como_1907\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a switch\", \"from\": 1916, \"to\": 1924}, {\"ngram\": \"the missing piece\", \"from\": 2037, \"to\": 2054}, {\"ngram\": \"the difference\", \"from\": 2065, \"to\": 2079}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cIt feels subtle,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099 he said.\", \"from\": 2082, \"to\": 2116, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cIt\", \"from\": 2082, \"to\": 2087}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI think since I have been working with Chris, there is been a few answers that he's had.\", \"from\": 2117, \"to\": 2208, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Chris\", \"from\": 2159, \"to\": 2164}, {\"ngram\": \"a few answers\", \"from\": 2180, \"to\": 2193}]}, {\"sentence\": \"My dad and I have talked about it.\", \"from\": 2209, \"to\": 2243, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My dad\", \"from\": 2209, \"to\": 2215}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is some answers that we need\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094or some questions we had that we did not really have some answers to, and Chris has got a really good background in biomechanics and has been coaching for a very long time.\", \"from\": 2244, \"to\": 2453, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some answers\", \"from\": 2253, \"to\": 2265}, {\"ngram\": \"some questions\", \"from\": 2284, \"to\": 2298}, {\"ngram\": \"some answers\", \"from\": 2334, \"to\": 2346}, {\"ngram\": \"Chris\", \"from\": 2355, \"to\": 2360}, {\"ngram\": \"a really good background\", \"from\": 2369, \"to\": 2393}, {\"ngram\": \"biomechanics\", \"from\": 2397, \"to\": 2409}, {\"ngram\": \"a very long time\", \"from\": 2436, \"to\": 2452}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All really good coaches, I have seen a lot of different things, and they are more likely to have an answer.\", \"from\": 2454, \"to\": 2561, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 2491, \"to\": 2496}, {\"ngram\": \"different things\", \"from\": 2500, \"to\": 2516}, {\"ngram\": \"an answer\", \"from\": 2551, \"to\": 2560}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cMy dad has only coached me\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094he was a teaching pro but he wasn't teaching any pros, really, for that matter, more kids.\", \"from\": 2563, \"to\": 2685, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cMy dad\", \"from\": 2563, \"to\": 2572}, {\"ngram\": \"me\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094he\", \"from\": 2590, \"to\": 2597}, {\"ngram\": \"a teaching\", \"from\": 2602, \"to\": 2612}, {\"ngram\": \"any pros\", \"from\": 2640, \"to\": 2648}, {\"ngram\": \"that matter\", \"from\": 2662, \"to\": 2673}, {\"ngram\": \", more kids\", \"from\": 2673, \"to\": 2684}]}, {\"sentence\": \"My dad loves working with kids.\", \"from\": 2686, \"to\": 2717, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My dad\", \"from\": 2686, \"to\": 2692}, {\"ngram\": \"kids\", \"from\": 2712, \"to\": 2716}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's why my dad is the \\\"I do not know how far I can take you\\\" type.\", \"from\": 2718, \"to\": 2787, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my dad\", \"from\": 2729, \"to\": 2735}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\" type\", \"from\": 2780, \"to\": 2786}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's why he had that feeling.\", \"from\": 2788, \"to\": 2819, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that feeling\", \"from\": 2806, \"to\": 2818}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's why it's really cool that we were able to make it as far as we made it.\", \"from\": 2820, \"to\": 2898, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cBut I think it feels subtle, the changes.\", \"from\": 2900, \"to\": 2944, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the changes\", \"from\": 2932, \"to\": 2943}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Even when I wasn't winning, I just said, I was going to keep putting myself in position until I got comfortable.\", \"from\": 2945, \"to\": 3057, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"position\", \"from\": 3024, \"to\": 3032}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was very uncomfortable still at the PGA but surprisingly more comfortable at the Open.\", \"from\": 3058, \"to\": 3146, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the PGA\", \"from\": 3092, \"to\": 3099}, {\"ngram\": \"the Open\", \"from\": 3137, \"to\": 3145}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I look back now on all the majors that I played in, the ones I won and all the ones I lost, and I think they all played a part in my success.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099 Schauffele, perhaps more than others, holds the Olympics in high regard.\", \"from\": 3147, \"to\": 3368, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all the majors\", \"from\": 3166, \"to\": 3180}, {\"ngram\": \"the ones\", \"from\": 3199, \"to\": 3207}, {\"ngram\": \"all the ones\", \"from\": 3218, \"to\": 3230}, {\"ngram\": \"a part\", \"from\": 3267, \"to\": 3273}, {\"ngram\": \"my success.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099 Schauffele\", \"from\": 3277, \"to\": 3305}, {\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 3325, \"to\": 3331}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 3339, \"to\": 3351}, {\"ngram\": \"high regard\", \"from\": 3355, \"to\": 3366}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His dad once dreamed of competing at a decathlete before an injury thwarted his dreams.\", \"from\": 3369, \"to\": 3456, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His dad\", \"from\": 3369, \"to\": 3376}, {\"ngram\": \"a decathlete\", \"from\": 3406, \"to\": 3418}, {\"ngram\": \"an injury\", \"from\": 3426, \"to\": 3435}, {\"ngram\": \"his dreams\", \"from\": 3445, \"to\": 3455}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That quest and their talks about it gave Xander a different perspective, one that has been missing for some in golf because an Olympic medal is not the pinnacle for golfers.\", \"from\": 3458, \"to\": 3631, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3499, \"end\": 3505, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xander_Schauffele\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.0430422861700584e-15, \"text\": \"Xander\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13156709\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resou