 you are a little bit older, you are watching Jack (Nicklaus) or Arnie (Palmer), the older legends of the game.\", \"from\": 3895, \"to\": 4069, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4004, \"end\": 4008, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Branning\", \"score\": 0.9997284170861677, \"rank\": 0.00023955901675316637, \"text\": \"Jack\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Branning\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Branning\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 3906, \"to\": 3911}, {\"ngram\": \"the kids\", \"from\": 3915, \"to\": 3923}, {\"ngram\": \"Tiger\", \"from\": 3938, \"to\": 3943}, {\"ngram\": \"Woods\", \"from\": 3945, \"to\": 3950}, {\"ngram\": \"(Nicklaus\", \"from\": 4009, \"to\": 4018}, {\"ngram\": \"Arnie\", \"from\": 4023, \"to\": 4028}, {\"ngram\": \"Palmer\", \"from\": 4030, \"to\": 4036}, {\"ngram\": \"the older legends\", \"from\": 4039, \"to\": 4056}, {\"ngram\": \"the game\", \"from\": 4060, \"to\": 4068}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You are watching them win majors.\", \"from\": 4070, \"to\": 4103, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"majors\", \"from\": 4096, \"to\": 4102}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cIt's kind of different.\", \"from\": 4105, \"to\": 4131, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For me it's very personal, my relationship with my dad, the relationship my dad and I have with golf ... his teachings of when he was trying to be an Olympian.\", \"from\": 4132, \"to\": 4291, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4282, \"end\": 4290, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999897995622, \"rank\": 1.020033051375285e-08, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my relationship\", \"from\": 4159, \"to\": 4174}, {\"ngram\": \"my dad\", \"from\": 4180